      <title>焦点：哥伦比亚政策导致投资降温，经济增长面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/colombia-policy-lurches-chill-investment-risk-economic-growth-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗的不可预测的政策波动导致投资大幅下降，预计今年这种情况将持续下去，因为一些企业主抱怨战略规划几乎变得不可能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/colombia-policy-lurches-chill-investment-risk-economic-growth-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 11:07:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
